This document discuss about application of Morse Code is real life


	Morse Code in Telecommunication:
	
	Samuel F.B.Morse invented Morse code methos used in telecommunication to encode text
	characters as standardized sequences of two different signals called 'dot' & 'dash'. 
	International morse code is known as 'Continential Morse Code'.
	
	Dot is measured as basic duration of time & duration of dash is 3 times of duration of dot.
	
	US navy intelligence trained their specialists to master this code.
	

